title: Madison Adjusts In Classic Win Over SF Christian
text:
Madison Adjusts In Classic Win Over SF Christian Bulldogs Win Battle Of Unbeatens Zach Borg , KDLT News Weekend Sports Anchor, z_borg@kdlt.com POSTED: 06:06 PM CDT Oct 04, 2015 UPDATED: 06:14 PM CDT Oct 04, 2015 Madison Wins Classic With SF Christian MADISON, S.D. - 
This week's Football Friday feature game between Madison and Sioux Falls Christian lived up to it's billing. The host Bulldogs rallied from down 20-7 at half to defeat the Chargers 32-26 in overtime in a battle of unbeaten teams. Click on the video viewer for highlights and reaction!
